Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.36,0:00:03.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k236}命运也是推理的线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.94,0:00:05.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k158}神秘的事件也能看得清清楚楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.00,0:00:07.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k206}今天是活跃的侦探团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.67,0:00:09.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k168}小孩画的图画是解谜的关键
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.08,0:00:11.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k241}唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.62,0:00:13.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k154}外表看似小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.47,0:00:15.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k185}他的名字就是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.99,0:00:17.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k252}Something's just not right
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.41,0:00:21.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在找寻着什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.46,0:00:26.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}已经习惯了谎言 现在也是一样 fake your eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.45,0:00:32.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}The start of century
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}没有能够确定的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.22,0:00:41.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}即使一个人也不能哭泣 软弱 hate myself
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.55,0:00:51.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}与真实的痛苦相反的是 埋藏在心中的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.53,0:00:59.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}现在 映射出来 朝着两个人所决定的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.12,0:01:03.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}I think it's only my destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.76,0:01:06.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}朝着没有尽头的黑暗前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.22,0:01:13.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那里有未知的明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.51,0:01:18.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Oh yeah. You're going nowhere. It's only destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.47,0:01:21.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}切实地前行着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.77,0:01:28.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}感受现在 you're in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.94,0:01:32.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}You're in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.06,0:01:58.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你画的还是那么糟 元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.94,0:02:02.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你自己也不怎么样嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.18,0:02:06.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}哼 无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.83,0:02:10.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k265}男子汉不靠画画好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.32,0:02:11.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过 还是画画好的好呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.29,0:02:18.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真向往啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.88,0:02:21.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k258}就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.62,0:02:24.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}我从明天开始上绘画课吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.45,0:02:26.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我也去 我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.15,0:02:29.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}真受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.81,0:02:43.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他在做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.55,0:02:44.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k174}可疑的老头子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.10,0:02:47.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k155}闻到了犯罪的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.42,0:02:58.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.68,0:02:59.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k126}钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.75,0:03:02.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k107}一大笔钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.43,0:03:07.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.55,0:03:08.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k112}难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.47,0:03:13.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}站住 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.68,0:03:15.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k121}那些钱是怎么来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}是不是偷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.13,0:03:20.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k237}不 不是 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.95,0:03:21.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k283}抓住他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.35,0:03:23.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k115}等一下 你们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.13,0:03:30.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}放开我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.53,0:03:31.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}小少爷 小少爷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.17,0:03:34.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k164}快要被杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.36,0:03:37.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k201}果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.64,0:03:46.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}图画中的绑架犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.59,0:04:08.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}果然让我猜对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.69,0:04:10.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.15,0:04:13.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k146}发生了绑架案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.71,0:04:20.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}被绑架的是燕氏财阀会长 燕健三的孙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.29,0:04:23.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}燕秋夫 5岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.20,0:04:26.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k291}他是一个很喜欢画画的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.57,0:04:33.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而那些钱是秋夫的赎金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.58,0:04:35.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那么 燕先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.38,0:04:38.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}请详细说明一下情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.55,0:04:40.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.22,0:04:42.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k168}燕先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.23,0:04:45.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.31,0:04:48.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k207}是秋夫画的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.69,0:04:51.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k239}绑架犯送来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.88,0:04:53.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什么时候送来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.37,0:04:56.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}昨天中午
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.70,0:05:00.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k233}和恐吓信一起扔在信箱里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.64,0:05:02.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这就是那封恐吓信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}孩子值十亿日元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.23,0:05:13.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k265}皮埃罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.27,0:05:17.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}好厉害 这能吃多少碗鳗鱼饭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}元太真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.74,0:05:23.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k186}但是刚才那些钱肯定没有十亿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.09,0:05:29.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那只是意思头金 看看你是不是真的想付钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}犯人当时肯定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.41,0:05:41.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.49,0:05:44.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.60,0:05:45.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}喂 你们几个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.12,0:05:47.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k151}谢谢你们来报案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.56,0:05:49.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k144}剩下的是警察的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.59,0:05:51.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k203}你们现在立即回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.21,0:05:54.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警部先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.43,0:05:57.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k122}你们警察也请回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.53,0:06:00.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是 燕先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.48,0:06:05.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}秋夫的父母去年死于交通事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.65,0:06:08.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他是我唯一的孙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.15,0:06:09.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}如果他发生了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.89,0:06:13.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k174}我对不起死去的儿子和儿媳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.46,0:06:16.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我能理解你的心情 燕先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.58,0:06:21.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是与犯人接头 交付赎金的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.88,0:06:24.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是逮捕犯人的最佳时机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.97,0:06:27.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}十亿日元也是很大的一笔钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.67,0:06:28.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}所以犯人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.07,0:06:29.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.25,0:06:32.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k118}抓不到犯人也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.28,0:06:36.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不能让秋夫有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.44,0:06:39.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且 我并没有把钱直接交给他的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.16,0:06:44.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.49,0:06:51.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天早上在信箱里发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.53,0:06:53.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}转账账户
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.32,0:06:57.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}瑞士方特贝尔银行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.69,0:07:00.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}瑞士银行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.51,0:07:04.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k282}警部 立即和银行联系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}让他们暂停转款 交出账户资料…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.06,0:07:09.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.09,0:07:12.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k202}瑞士是银行之国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.43,0:07:17.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k235}要是能这样的话 瑞士银行的时代就不会存在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.89,0:07:19.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.21,0:07:21.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k131}让我说两句吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.22,0:07:24.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个孩子说的对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.89,0:07:27.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k267}他们不管遇到什么情况也不会破例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.61,0:07:31.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k273}不过 只要秋夫能回来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.64,0:07:33.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}求求你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.75,0:07:34.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}请回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.91,0:07:38.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}老爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.43,0:07:42.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.89,0:07:43.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k146}这个就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.13,0:07:45.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k124}成功犯罪了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.01,0:07:53.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警部先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.18,0:07:57.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k116}难道真的不继续查了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.93,0:07:58.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}当然要查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k148}犯人绑架孩子勒索燕先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.84,0:08:05.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k243}计划将赎金转账到瑞士银行的方法也万无一失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.41,0:08:06.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是作为警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.98,0:08:10.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k156}不能眼看着这样的恶性犯罪发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.86,0:08:13.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你是要等燕先生付了赎金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.25,0:08:18.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k239}秋夫平安回来后 再开始搜查吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.77,0:08:19.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.70,0:08:26.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是 即使付了赎金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.60,0:08:29.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}秋夫也不一定能平安回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.51,0:08:37.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}秋夫真的很喜欢画画啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.61,0:08:42.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.53,0:08:51.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.34,0:08:53.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k281}柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.52,0:08:59.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}老爷爷 刚才那张秋夫的画再借我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.72,0:09:06.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}果然这张也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.87,0:09:09.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k214}哦 那个是秋夫的怪癖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.26,0:09:11.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怪癖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.54,0:09:16.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k129}他画画的时候 总把那时看见的东西当做签名画上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看见的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.15,0:09:23.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}说起来 好像在哪里看到过相同的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真的 在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.83,0:09:30.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}哦 对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.68,0:09:37.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}是上次在秋夫上的米花南幼儿园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.58,0:09:40.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看了他画的画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.77,0:09:42.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}米花南幼儿园吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k254}老爷爷 这张画借给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.03,0:09:46.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}我一定还回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.88,0:09:48.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k185}喂 孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.61,0:09:57.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}打扰一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.68,0:09:59.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k207}什么事 孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k177}我想看看燕秋夫画的画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.66,0:10:06.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}秋夫的画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.53,0:10:13.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}秋夫爷爷看到的画 应该在这里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.86,0:10:15.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.84,0:10:18.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k198}就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.75,0:10:23.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k291}老师 秋夫是在哪里画的这张画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.47,0:10:30.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}肯定没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.08,0:10:34.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k161}那个签名和秋夫在这里画的签名一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.23,0:10:39.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且 送来的画是在监禁的地方画的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.17,0:10:45.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也就是说 知道了这个签名所画东西的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.77,0:10:48.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就能找到秋夫被监禁的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.25,0:10:51.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是问题是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.45,0:10:52.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k121}柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.51,0:10:55.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}你在干什么 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}不许吃独食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.57,0:10:58.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k219}我没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k173}别装蒜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.63,0:11:03.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k133}就是 你是不是想一个人去救秋夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.19,0:11:05.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我们也要来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.24,0:11:07.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}别说傻话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.09,0:11:10.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k185}对方是绑架犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.70,0:11:12.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k261}你们知道有多危险吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.30,0:11:12.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k161}可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.94,0:11:14.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k164}你们看看这张画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.04,0:11:16.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}秋夫看上去很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.71,0:11:17.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k167}嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.91,0:11:21.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}好像和犯人在高高兴兴地看电视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.21,0:11:24.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是啊 这不是假面超人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}光看这张画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.59,0:11:28.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k158}他好像暂时还没有什么危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.17,0:11:30.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k258}要救人就要趁现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.16,0:11:31.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k199}嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.62,0:11:34.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k146}柯南也是这样想的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.67,0:11:37.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你们啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.74,0:11:40.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k207}而且 这起案子也是我们一起发现的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.27,0:11:42.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是 就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.65,0:11:45.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.20,0:11:49.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k156}不过 我们只负责找监禁地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.27,0:11:51.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}找到之后的事情就交给警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.73,0:11:52.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k246}好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.68,0:11:55.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}这是个签名啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.00,0:11:56.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k132}原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k161}可是 这画的是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.80,0:12:02.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是外星人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.43,0:12:03.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k164}是烟囱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.00,0:12:05.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k157}建筑物上面的烟囱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.52,0:12:08.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k252}绝对是外星人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.60,0:12:11.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}这里怎么会看见外星人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.55,0:12:14.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}不过 这里也看不到烟囱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k215}没时间吵架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.14,0:12:21.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}烟囱也好 大楼也好 什么都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.83,0:12:24.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k269}只要像这个签名的都行 大家分头去找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.73,0:12:25.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.08,0:12:47.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.21,0:12:50.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真的吗 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.79,0:12:53.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k258}看 不就是那个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.94,0:12:57.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}水塔 但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.78,0:13:00.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k283}说像也像 说不像也不像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.55,0:13:03.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k277}不 恐怕就是它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.36,0:13:05.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.27,0:13:08.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}为什么这么肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.53,0:13:10.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.08,0:13:13.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k156}那个水塔前面还能看见什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.74,0:13:18.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有个大钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k216}那是个公园吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.31,0:13:23.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那又怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.80,0:13:26.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k149}签名上没有画公园啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.46,0:13:27.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k265}你们仔细看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.53,0:13:32.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}签名中间有个像眼睛一样的东西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.92,0:13:33.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.70,0:13:35.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k177}确实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.09,0:13:39.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k239}水塔和大钟重叠起来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.95,0:13:41.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}看上去会是什么样子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.63,0:13:44.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.73,0:13:46.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}签名上画的 像眼睛一样的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.06,0:13:48.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k233}就是那个大钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.98,0:13:52.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}这么说 秋夫就在那个水塔里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.68,0:13:58.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不对 秋夫是在能看见大钟和水塔重合的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.70,0:13:59.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.13,0:14:03.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k143}那么 去那个水塔看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.38,0:14:06.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}说不定能发现他所在的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.96,0:14:08.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好 我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.02,0:14:23.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么样 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.67,0:14:27.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k266}那里就是刚才看见的那个有大钟的公园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.61,0:14:31.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}秋夫签名上的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.17,0:14:35.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k256}正好画在水塔正中间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.15,0:14:36.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.72,0:14:39.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k158}就算有点误差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.10,0:14:44.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k237}秋夫也应该被监禁在这一带的某处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.06,0:14:48.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有这么多房子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.44,0:14:52.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k238}果然 从这里也看不出什么来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.07,0:14:55.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大家分头找 很快就能找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.49,0:14:57.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.69,0:14:59.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k119}那么试试看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.01,0:15:07.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一旦发现可疑的人和可疑的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.10,0:15:09.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就立即用侦探徽章跟其他人联系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.05,0:15:13.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}绝对不要独自行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.34,0:15:15.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k229}把秋夫救出来才是最重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.46,0:15:41.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.00,0:15:44.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k154}有不少可疑的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.70,0:15:47.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k269}可是都不能确定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.93,0:15:51.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可疑的目标还是太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.50,0:15:54.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}说起来步美呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.51,0:15:59.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}应该是五点在公园集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂 我是步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.97,0:16:08.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k227}步美 你现在在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.09,0:16:11.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.75,0:16:14.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k166}我想秋夫是不是饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.89,0:16:16.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就到便利店买了点东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.84,0:16:18.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}真是受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.06,0:16:21.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k223}集合时间已经过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.38,0:16:23.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.37,0:16:26.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k199}马上就去 再等一会儿…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.93,0:16:32.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}皮埃罗的面具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.47,0:16:34.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k254}你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k167}我听不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.59,0:16:41.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}步美 发生了什么事
